title: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of sync
description: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of sync
OB: When exporting a directory (project) and placing the exported jar in the same directory (project), an out of sync message is displayed when overwriting the exported jarfile the second time.
SR:
To reproduce:
1. Export a directory (project).
2. Place the exported jar in the same directory (project).
3. Overwrite the exported jarfile.
